item.title: Erding
item.description: Route It tooks an hour to ride from Neufahrn to Erding, ridden along the Isar River and then passed by the Munich Airport, which is the highlight of this journey. Routing City Erding is a town in Bavaria, Germany, and capital of the district Erding. It had a population of 36,469 in 2019. The original Erdinger Weissbier is a well-known Bavarian specialty.
